            <description><![CDATA[今天，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E7%99%8C%E7%97%87%E6%97%A5%23&amp;isnewpage=1" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#世界癌症日#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[奥特曼]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_aoteman-7ddbc90d1c.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br><br>世界卫生组织认为三分之一的癌症是可以预防的。而防癌体检可早期发现大部分常见癌症<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[举手]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/fd/2022_raisehand_org.png" data-rsshub-image="href" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> 防癌体检有哪些？不同的部位该做什么检查？和卫一起了解👇🏻 <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视新闻） <img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hmhi1owhfej20u022gndq.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hmhi1odhpcj20u01sxwth.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hmhi1oeyeej20u01xwto8.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hmhi1ogn18j20u01xw4ev.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hmhi1oht8fj20u02ao7pb.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hmhi1oj37gj20u02ao1dh.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hmhi1ojdirj20u0272wz5.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hmhi1ojhbyj20u024fwy1.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="http